          unfold nf_matrix; ext i j; fin_cases i <;> fin_cases j <;> norm_num <;> ring;
      -- Since the identity matrix is positive definite, the inequality 0 ≤ (2 * lam * mu - γ * lam^2 * mu) • 1 holds if and only if 2 * lam * mu - γ * lam^2 * mu ≥ 0.
